務める多聞丸だった。"},{"id":1089311,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1089311","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"旋律","duration":"00:26:00","airdate":"2022-05-31","comment":7,"desc":"呂蒙は徐福院の地下に広がる不思議な空間で目を覚ます。\r\nそこは、この世と霊界の狭間にある黄泉比良坂。\r\n蘇った亡霊・呂布との悲しみの対決を乗り越えた呂蒙だったが、\r\nその時、ついに霊界から亡者の群れが一斉に溢れ出す。\r\n佐々木巌流と多聞丸の二人と手を組んだ呂蒙は、生きて外の世界に戻るため、\r\n大地を埋め尽くすほどの亡者の群れに立ち向かう。"},{"id":1089313,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1089313","type":1,"sort":0,"name":"放送直前特番","duration":"","airdate":"2022-05-10","comment":1,"desc":""}],"crt":[{"id":3325,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c8/69/3325_crt_u24Ex.jpg","name":"孫策伯符","desc":"浅野真澄"},{"id":3326,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/37/18/3326_crt_B45zd.jpg","name":"呂蒙子明","desc":"甲斐田裕子"},{"id":3330,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/99/a3/3330_crt_3ZPpy.jpg","name":"楽就","desc":"飯島肇"},{"id":3342,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8c/91/3342_crt_XYJxr.jpg","name":"関羽雲長","desc":"生天目仁美"},{"id":21723,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ac/15/21723_crt_rQRCs.jpg","name":"呂布奉先","desc":"渡辺明乃"},{"id":67696,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/86/f3/67696_crt_6IWV2.jpg","name":"諸葛亮孔明","desc":"門脇舞以"},{"id":67697,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/54/7f/67697_crt_mjVR2.jpg","name":"趙雲子龍","desc":"浅川悠"},{"id":108851,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/65/4a/108851_crt_VyJnB.jpg","name":"孫権仲謀","desc":"大橋彩香"},{"id":109165,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e5/9c/109165_crt_Kbp8x.jpg","name":"山田朝右衛門","desc":"種﨑敦美"}],"staff":[{"id":220,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ec/8c/220_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"ジェンコ","desc":"製作"},{"id":7503,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e4/31/7503_prsn_JQqv2.jpg","name":"少年画報社","desc":"製作"},{"id":230,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/86/230_prsn_ur466.jpg","name":"AT-X","desc":"製作"},{"id":220,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ec/8c/220_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"ジェンコ","desc":"制作"},{"id":1436,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b1/54/1436_prsn_Gjc0N.jpg","name":"ARMS","desc":"动画制作"},{"id":19478,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d7/9e/19478_prsn_H5I52.jpg","name":"一居一平","desc":"原画"},{"id":1930